1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 26]

2
00:00:18,653 --> 00:00:19,332
Objection!

3
00:00:19,653 --> 00:00:21,452
Such speculative conjecture!

4
00:00:21,813 --> 00:00:22,732
May I ask the opposing counsel

5
00:00:23,013 --> 00:00:24,372
what evidence you have to prove that

6
00:00:25,013 --> 00:00:26,972
Nanxi visited Chuxue that night?

7
00:00:26,973 --> 00:00:28,012
The Zhou residence has a witness

8
00:00:28,013 --> 00:00:29,052
who claims to have seen Nanxi

9
00:00:29,053 --> 00:00:30,532
entering Chuxue's room that evening.

10
00:00:30,813 --> 00:00:31,932
I went to see her

11
00:00:32,053 --> 00:00:33,972
because Chuxue and I were close friends.

12
00:00:34,973 --> 00:00:36,372
But I didn't see her that night.

13
00:00:36,653 --> 00:00:38,012
So I went to check on her.

14
00:00:39,013 --> 00:00:40,292
She refused to see me.

15
00:00:40,733 --> 00:00:41,892
How can you claim

16
00:00:42,093 --> 00:00:43,892
that I told her to go to the back hill?

17
00:00:44,373 --> 00:00:45,332
Besides,

18
00:00:45,653 --> 00:00:46,972
the entire Zhou residence

19
00:00:47,773 --> 00:00:48,972
is filled with his people.

20
00:00:49,093 --> 00:00:51,092
There's no possibility of objective corroboration.

21
00:00:51,573 --> 00:00:52,412
Objection sustained.

22
00:00:56,013 --> 00:00:56,572
Then

23
00:00:56,853 --> 00:00:58,052
this piece of evidence

24
00:00:58,333 --> 00:00:59,332
is now crucial.

25
00:01:06,573 --> 00:01:07,932
This surgical consent form

26
00:01:07,933 --> 00:01:09,012
has illegible handwriting.

27
00:01:14,573 --> 00:01:15,292
Your Honor,

28
00:01:15,573 --> 00:01:16,612
I possess a copy

29
00:01:16,773 --> 00:01:17,932
of the surgical consent form

30
00:01:17,933 --> 00:01:19,652
from the day of the surgery.

31
00:01:25,773 --> 00:01:26,492
Please examine this.

32
00:01:26,573 --> 00:01:28,412
The handwriting matches exactly on the carbon copy.

33
00:01:29,053 --> 00:01:30,052
The ink impression

34
00:01:30,213 --> 00:01:31,292
is also identical.

35
00:01:33,693 --> 00:01:34,212
Evidence

36
00:01:34,213 --> 00:01:35,052
admitted.

37
00:01:36,013 --> 00:01:37,492
Nanxi's left-handed handwriting

38
00:01:37,573 --> 00:01:39,292
comes from her surgical signature.

39
00:01:39,413 --> 00:01:40,652
She is left-handed

40
00:01:40,653 --> 00:01:42,292
but never writes with her left hand.

41
00:01:42,853 --> 00:01:44,132
Because she only uses it

42
00:01:45,693 --> 00:01:47,412
for criminal acts.

43
00:01:47,573 --> 00:01:48,932
Her left-handed handwriting is completely

44
00:01:48,933 --> 00:01:50,772
different from her right-handed script.

45
00:01:52,853 --> 00:01:53,572
May I ask,

46
00:01:53,573 --> 00:01:54,412
Ms. Ye,

47
00:01:55,053 --> 00:01:57,052
where did you obtain

48
00:01:57,053 --> 00:01:58,212
this surgical consent form?

49
00:01:58,293 --> 00:01:59,052
From the hospital.

50
00:01:59,213 --> 00:02:00,332
To my knowledge,

51
00:02:00,853 --> 00:02:03,132
this document was submitted to the police station.

52
00:02:03,213 --> 00:02:05,132
How did it end up in your possession?

53
00:02:05,573 --> 00:02:06,772
As you can see,

54
00:02:07,853 --> 00:02:09,012
this consent form

55
00:02:09,693 --> 00:02:11,452
was nearly destroyed at the police station.

56
00:02:12,253 --> 00:02:14,132
I retrieved it from an officer's hands.

57
00:02:14,693 --> 00:02:15,412
Is that so?

58
00:02:15,693 --> 00:02:16,852
This is the surgical consent form

59
00:02:16,853 --> 00:02:19,292
provided by the police.

60
00:02:20,013 --> 00:02:21,292
Where did yours come from?

61
00:02:23,133 --> 00:02:23,892
Impossible!

62
00:02:25,413 --> 00:02:26,292
Your Honor,

63
00:02:27,453 --> 00:02:28,692
his document is forged.

64
00:02:28,813 --> 00:02:29,532
Authenticity

65
00:02:29,813 --> 00:02:31,132
can be verified by witnesses.

66
00:02:31,293 --> 00:02:32,092
Your Honor,

67
00:02:32,413 --> 00:02:34,012
I request to summon

68
00:02:34,133 --> 00:02:35,532
another key figure in this case:

69
00:02:36,053 --> 00:02:37,532
the director of the Hospital,

70
00:02:37,893 --> 00:02:38,692
Lin Huaidong.

71
00:02:39,973 --> 00:02:40,692
Granted.

72
00:02:42,573 --> 00:02:42,892


73
00:02:42,893 --> 00:02:43,292


74
00:02:43,413 --> 00:02:43,852


75
00:02:43,853 --> 00:02:44,212


76
00:02:48,013 --> 00:02:48,692
Director Lin,

77
00:02:49,253 --> 00:02:50,612
of these two surgical consent forms,

78
00:02:51,013 --> 00:02:53,132
which one bears Miss Nanxi's handwriting?

79
00:02:56,293 --> 00:02:57,612
It's this one.

80
00:02:57,973 --> 00:03:00,012
It has my signature.

81
00:03:03,733 --> 00:03:04,452
Director Lin.

82
00:03:05,733 --> 00:03:06,572
Director Lin!

83
00:03:08,293 --> 00:03:09,292
That's not true.

84
00:03:09,693 --> 00:03:10,412
Your Honor.

85
00:03:11,173 --> 00:03:11,852
Director Lin was

86
00:03:11,853 --> 00:03:13,012
Nanxi's attending physician

87
00:03:13,413 --> 00:03:15,532
on the day she gave birth.

88
00:03:15,893 --> 00:03:17,012
This surgical consent form

89
00:03:17,293 --> 00:03:18,452
in my possession

90
00:03:18,693 --> 00:03:20,292
was provided by him.

91
00:03:20,973 --> 00:03:23,852
Ms. Ye previously submitted

92
00:03:23,973 --> 00:03:25,732
so-called evidence to the police,

93
00:03:25,733 --> 00:03:26,732
yet now produces

94
00:03:26,733 --> 00:03:28,172
an unburned piece of evidence.

95
00:03:28,173 --> 00:03:28,852
I ask,

96
00:03:29,013 --> 00:03:30,012
does such evidence

97
00:03:30,013 --> 00:03:31,292
hold credibility?

98
00:03:31,533 --> 00:03:32,252
If

99
00:03:32,813 --> 00:03:34,132
I could provide false evidence,

100
00:03:34,613 --> 00:03:35,892
then isn't it possible

101
00:03:35,893 --> 00:03:37,572
that Director Lin did the same?

102
00:03:37,733 --> 00:03:38,412
Then

103
00:03:38,573 --> 00:03:40,092
shouldn't we consider

104
00:03:40,093 --> 00:03:42,412
this so-called key evidence

105
00:03:42,733 --> 00:03:43,852
invalid?

106
00:03:48,613 --> 00:03:49,452
Your Honor,

107
00:03:50,013 --> 00:03:52,892
I believe Ms. Lin provided false evidence

108
00:03:53,013 --> 00:03:54,532
to obstruct the trial process,

109
00:03:54,533 --> 00:03:56,812
in contempt of court.

110
00:04:09,413 --> 00:04:10,292
I hereby declare that

111
00:04:10,293 --> 00:04:11,012
Nanxi,

112
00:04:11,013 --> 00:04:13,292
suspected of murdering Ye Chuxue,

113
00:04:13,613 --> 00:04:15,012
is to be released immediately

114
00:04:15,253 --> 00:04:16,252
due to insufficient evidence.

115
00:04:40,493 --> 00:04:41,372
What's wrong?

116
00:04:41,493 --> 00:04:42,732
Ms. Ye?

117
00:04:44,733 --> 00:04:46,492
You will pay for what you've done,

118
00:04:46,493 --> 00:04:47,732
I swear it.

119
00:04:51,933 --> 00:04:53,372
I've already lost everything.

120
00:04:54,733 --> 00:04:56,052
What more can I pay?

121
00:04:56,853 --> 00:04:57,732
Not enough.

122
00:04:58,733 --> 00:04:59,732
Far from enough.

123
00:05:05,053 --> 00:05:05,932
How dare you leave?

124
00:05:06,373 --> 00:05:07,052
Where are you going?

125
00:05:08,373 --> 00:05:08,932
Zhiqiu!

126
00:05:08,933 --> 00:05:09,732
Where are you going?
- Zhiqiu!

127
00:05:09,933 --> 00:05:10,612
Let her go.

128
00:05:26,613 --> 00:05:27,372
Zhou Yimo.

129
00:05:30,373 --> 00:05:31,372
I can't accept this.

130
00:05:31,813 --> 00:05:32,732
I know.

131
00:05:33,293 --> 00:05:34,052
Don't worry.

132
00:05:34,613 --> 00:05:35,852
I've already sent someone to follow her.

133
00:05:38,053 --> 00:05:39,172
Especially at times like this,

134
00:05:39,933 --> 00:05:41,012
we must stay calm.

135
00:05:41,253 --> 00:05:42,052
Okay?

136
00:05:45,733 --> 00:05:47,612
Director Lin's family was threatened by the police,

137
00:05:48,293 --> 00:05:49,492
forcing him to commit perjury.

138
00:05:52,373 --> 00:05:53,372
The police...

139
00:05:56,733 --> 00:05:57,492
I understand.

140
00:05:59,053 --> 00:06:00,052
Nanxi must possess

141
00:06:01,173 --> 00:06:03,492
concrete evidence against Zhou Quan.

142
00:06:04,253 --> 00:06:05,172
That's why Zhou Quan

143
00:06:06,053 --> 00:06:07,612
is protecting her at all costs.

144
00:06:08,493 --> 00:06:09,172
Exactly.

145
00:06:11,173 --> 00:06:12,172
To take her down,

146
00:06:12,933 --> 00:06:14,292
we must root my uncle out completely.

147
00:06:14,853 --> 00:06:15,932
out completely.

148
00:06:20,293 --> 00:06:20,812
It's fine.

149
00:06:20,813 --> 00:06:21,612
Don't worry.

150
00:06:22,733 --> 00:06:23,732
Leave it to me.

151
00:07:01,613 --> 00:07:02,932
Why are you at the Zhou residence?

152
00:07:03,173 --> 00:07:03,852
Get out.

153
00:07:04,293 --> 00:07:05,732
Did Nanxi kill you?

154
00:07:07,133 --> 00:07:07,812
Isn't that right?

155
00:07:09,493 --> 00:07:10,492
Tell me.

156
00:07:12,253 --> 00:07:13,492
So what if she did?

157
00:07:14,853 --> 00:07:15,732
My death

158
00:07:16,053 --> 00:07:16,932
has already ruined

159
00:07:16,933 --> 00:07:18,492
the bright future you deserved.

160
00:07:19,253 --> 00:07:20,612
Don't destroy yourself too.

161
00:07:20,613 --> 00:07:21,732
Get out of here.

162
00:07:21,733 --> 00:07:22,292
No!

163
00:07:23,613 --> 00:07:24,612
I made a vow.

164
00:07:25,173 --> 00:07:26,492
Every person who hurt you

165
00:07:27,573 --> 00:07:29,172
will pay the price.

166
00:07:30,613 --> 00:07:32,572
Is this my obsession,

167
00:07:33,053 --> 00:07:34,812
or is it yours?

168
00:07:35,373 --> 00:07:36,292
It's mine.

169
00:07:38,493 --> 00:07:39,372
I admit it.

170
00:07:43,053 --> 00:07:45,012
You gave up your studies and future

171
00:07:46,053 --> 00:07:47,172
to support my education.

172
00:07:49,053 --> 00:07:50,492
You lifted me up.

173
00:07:51,493 --> 00:07:53,492
I feel guilty. I feel ashamed.

174
00:07:56,173 --> 00:07:57,812
All my efforts

175
00:07:59,373 --> 00:08:00,492
were to ensure you

176
00:08:00,493 --> 00:08:02,252
lived the finest life.

177
00:08:03,613 --> 00:08:04,572
But Nanxi...

178
00:08:05,573 --> 00:08:07,172
Nanxi destroyed everything.

179
00:08:07,733 --> 00:08:09,052
She shattered my dreams.

180
00:08:12,253 --> 00:08:14,372
You've been wrong all along.

181
00:08:16,493 --> 00:08:17,292
People

182
00:08:18,173 --> 00:08:19,812
should live for themselves.

183
00:08:23,173 --> 00:08:24,812
When I gave up my studies,

184
00:08:24,813 --> 00:08:26,412
it wasn't just for you!

185
00:08:28,373 --> 00:08:29,492
Because I studied,

186
00:08:30,293 --> 00:08:32,252
I know not everyone

187
00:08:32,253 --> 00:08:33,852
is as naturally gifted as you.

188
00:08:34,133 --> 00:08:36,132
Not everyone excels effortlessly.

189
00:08:38,013 --> 00:08:38,732
No, that's not true.

190
00:08:42,093 --> 00:08:43,452
That's just your excuse.

191
00:08:52,493 --> 00:08:53,132
Sister.

192
00:08:56,213 --> 00:08:56,852
Sister.

193
00:09:11,853 --> 00:09:12,852
Is anyone here?

194
00:09:14,373 --> 00:09:15,492
Is Ms. Ye present?

195
00:09:31,133 --> 00:09:32,012
What are you doing?

196
00:09:32,213 --> 00:09:32,972
Why are you arresting me?

197
00:09:32,973 --> 00:09:33,732
Ms. Ye,

198
00:09:33,853 --> 00:09:35,092
we've received reports

199
00:09:35,253 --> 00:09:36,732
that you abused your position

200
00:09:36,733 --> 00:09:37,652
to misuse medications

201
00:09:37,853 --> 00:09:39,212
during patient surgeries,

202
00:09:39,493 --> 00:09:40,772
causing irreversible

203
00:09:40,773 --> 00:09:42,012
physical side effects.

204
00:09:43,333 --> 00:09:44,252
Misuse of medications?

205
00:09:54,493 --> 00:09:55,132
Master,

206
00:09:55,373 --> 00:09:56,612
we dispatched multiple teams

207
00:09:56,613 --> 00:09:57,732
to track Nanxi,

208
00:09:58,533 --> 00:10:00,012
but police interfered each time.

209
00:10:00,373 --> 00:10:02,252
It seems Nanxi possesses evidence

210
00:10:02,613 --> 00:10:04,492
that could destroy Zhou Quan.

211
00:10:05,453 --> 00:10:06,852
This could eliminate

212
00:10:07,093 --> 00:10:08,012
the final obstacle

213
00:10:08,013 --> 00:10:09,612
to overthrowing the Zhou family.

214
00:10:10,613 --> 00:10:11,252
Sir!

215
00:10:11,253 --> 00:10:11,892
Bad news!

216
00:10:12,093 --> 00:10:13,892
Ms. Ye has been arrested by the police.

217
00:10:15,733 --> 00:10:16,332
Let's go!

218
00:10:27,493 --> 00:10:28,612
A hundred thousand silver yuan

219
00:10:29,973 --> 00:10:31,012
to bail out Ye Zhiqiu.

220
00:10:31,133 --> 00:10:31,852
Is that enough?

221
00:10:33,133 --> 00:10:33,932
Mr. Zhou,

222
00:10:34,093 --> 00:10:35,372
technically speaking,

223
00:10:35,733 --> 00:10:36,732
it should be sufficient,

224
00:10:36,853 --> 00:10:38,372
but I'm not authorized to decide.

225
00:10:38,653 --> 00:10:39,372
Perhaps

226
00:10:39,853 --> 00:10:40,612
you should wait.

227
00:10:42,373 --> 00:10:43,492
Nephew.

228
00:10:48,453 --> 00:10:50,492
I let you go last time.

229
00:10:51,133 --> 00:10:53,492
Why are you pursuing me so relentlessly?

230
00:10:53,653 --> 00:10:55,732
Is this money enough to bail out Ye Zhiqiu?

231
00:10:55,733 --> 00:10:57,252
Of course it's enough.

232
00:10:58,893 --> 00:11:00,332
But, nephew,

233
00:11:00,333 --> 00:11:01,892
it's not about the money.

234
00:11:02,253 --> 00:11:03,892
The doctor's misuse of medication

235
00:11:03,893 --> 00:11:05,972
affects the hospital's reputation

236
00:11:05,973 --> 00:11:07,332
and raises safety concerns.

237
00:11:07,533 --> 00:11:11,132
Honestly, I'm willing but unable to help.

238
00:11:13,853 --> 00:11:14,492
Who is it?

239
00:11:17,013 --> 00:11:17,972
Lieutenant Yu.

240
00:11:19,013 --> 00:11:21,132
You always love playing jokes on me like this.

241
00:11:21,373 --> 00:11:22,852
How does a busy man like you have time

242
00:11:22,853 --> 00:11:24,732
to come to my small police station?

243
00:11:24,853 --> 00:11:25,972
Of course, to pick up

244
00:11:26,373 --> 00:11:27,492
my childhood sweetheart,

245
00:11:27,733 --> 00:11:29,012
Ms. Ye Zhiqiu.

246
00:11:29,893 --> 00:11:31,332
I heard she got into some trouble.

247
00:11:31,373 --> 00:11:33,772
It's no major case involving life or death.

248
00:11:34,613 --> 00:11:36,372
How can you bully her like this?

249
00:11:36,893 --> 00:11:37,732
Lieutenant Yu,

250
00:11:37,853 --> 00:11:39,252
don't be angry.

251
00:11:41,533 --> 00:11:43,732
Let's discuss this calmly, shall we?

252
00:11:43,733 --> 00:11:44,372
Right?

253
00:11:47,373 --> 00:11:48,772
What's there to discuss?

254
00:11:49,013 --> 00:11:49,892
If you don't release her,

255
00:11:49,893 --> 00:11:51,012
I'll break into the prison.

256
00:11:51,453 --> 00:11:52,252
After breaking in,

257
00:11:53,213 --> 00:11:54,892
wouldn't that embarrass you?

258
00:11:56,453 --> 00:11:57,372
I'll release her!

259
00:11:58,093 --> 00:11:59,132
Quickly! Release her!

260
00:11:59,933 --> 00:12:00,732
Yes, Chief Zhou.

261
00:12:00,733 --> 00:12:01,372
But...

262
00:12:01,653 --> 00:12:03,252
What about the money now?

263
00:12:04,253 --> 00:12:05,252
This...

264
00:12:06,133 --> 00:12:07,372
Since it's bail,

265
00:12:07,893 --> 00:12:08,772
not taking money

266
00:12:09,013 --> 00:12:10,212
doesn't make sense for you.

267
00:12:11,253 --> 00:12:12,732
Anyway, it's not mine.

268
00:12:13,373 --> 00:12:14,132
Fine.

269
00:12:14,533 --> 00:12:16,452
Put it down, put it down.

270
00:12:16,893 --> 00:12:17,532
Quickly!

271
00:12:18,013 --> 00:12:19,092
Wait a moment, wait.

272
00:12:50,093 --> 00:12:50,772
Zhiqiu!
- Xiaoman!

273
00:13:13,453 --> 00:13:16,092
[Zhou's residence]

274
00:13:16,133 --> 00:13:17,532
She suffered some external injuries.

275
00:13:17,893 --> 00:13:18,772
After taking those medicines,

276
00:13:18,773 --> 00:13:19,892
she'll recover soon.

277
00:13:21,013 --> 00:13:22,892
These are wounds from torture.

278
00:13:23,213 --> 00:13:24,532
But you only prescribe white tea ointment?

279
00:13:25,493 --> 00:13:27,252
While it takes its time healing wounds,

280
00:13:27,773 --> 00:13:29,012
but to prevent scarring,

281
00:13:29,013 --> 00:13:30,252
it's the best choice.

282
00:13:32,253 --> 00:13:33,132
Then white tea ointment it is.

283
00:13:34,093 --> 00:13:35,012
I'll get the medicine.

284
00:13:40,653 --> 00:13:41,452
Awake?

285
00:13:43,893 --> 00:13:44,772
How do you feel?

286
00:13:53,133 --> 00:13:54,772
Where is Lieutenant Yu?

287
00:14:02,373 --> 00:14:02,772
He...

288
00:14:02,893 --> 00:14:03,732
He's not here.

289
00:14:07,133 --> 00:14:08,132
I just...

290
00:14:08,893 --> 00:14:11,092
wanted to thank him in person.

291
00:14:11,893 --> 00:14:12,852
What about me?

292
00:14:16,773 --> 00:14:18,252
Of course, thank you too.

293
00:14:24,013 --> 00:14:25,652
It's my fault.

294
00:14:27,013 --> 00:14:28,332
I shouldn't have brought this up.

295
00:14:29,373 --> 00:14:30,132
It's alright.

296
00:14:32,653 --> 00:14:33,372
Nanxi.

297
00:14:34,453 --> 00:14:36,772
After Zhou Quan learned I sent people to follow her,

298
00:14:37,253 --> 00:14:38,652
he dispatched several more teams.

299
00:14:39,493 --> 00:14:40,892
They took her away.

300
00:14:42,253 --> 00:14:43,532
What about the driver Zhang Jinbao?

301
00:14:43,893 --> 00:14:45,332
We've been tracking him consistently.

302
00:14:46,013 --> 00:14:47,652
He didn't take the child back to his hometown.

303
00:14:48,213 --> 00:14:49,012
He changed his name

304
00:14:49,253 --> 00:14:50,892
and stayed in Wu County with his mother.

305
00:14:52,493 --> 00:14:55,012
Now he's a freight driver at Lu's Wharf.

306
00:14:55,373 --> 00:14:56,732
His mother takes care of the child.

307
00:14:57,453 --> 00:14:59,132
Nanxi knows we're watching her closely,

308
00:14:59,893 --> 00:15:01,732
but she won't go looking for Zhang Jinbao.

309
00:15:03,733 --> 00:15:04,612
Looks like

310
00:15:05,493 --> 00:15:06,372
we've found a way.

311
00:15:07,093 --> 00:15:08,852
She used to be someone who never missed a detail,

312
00:15:10,533 --> 00:15:11,492
but now

313
00:15:13,973 --> 00:15:15,092
she has a weakness.

314
00:15:18,133 --> 00:15:19,652
Change the dressing over here.

315
00:15:21,653 --> 00:15:22,852
Come on, give me a hand.

316
00:15:24,333 --> 00:15:25,132
Be careful.

317
00:15:25,133 --> 00:15:25,692
[Pediatrics]

318
00:15:25,733 --> 00:15:26,492
Take it slow.

319
00:15:26,533 --> 00:15:27,452
You go upstairs.

320
00:15:27,453 --> 00:15:27,812
[Pediatrics]

321
00:15:32,613 --> 00:15:33,892
What are you doing here?

322
00:15:34,013 --> 00:15:34,732
Baby.

323
00:15:39,253 --> 00:15:40,492
I asked the police

324
00:15:40,493 --> 00:15:41,892
to keep an eye on the child for me.

325
00:15:42,373 --> 00:15:43,892
Actually, we're doing fine.

326
00:15:44,013 --> 00:15:46,012
You should focus on your own safety.

327
00:15:46,733 --> 00:15:47,652
I'm fine.

328
00:15:48,013 --> 00:15:49,132
Don't worry about me.

329
00:15:49,253 --> 00:15:50,012
Granny.

330
00:15:50,493 --> 00:15:52,332
How many more days does the baby need to stay in the hospital?

331
00:15:52,853 --> 00:15:53,652
At least another

332
00:15:53,653 --> 00:15:56,252
three or four days before we can go home.

333
00:15:58,093 --> 00:15:58,732
Baby.

334
00:16:00,653 --> 00:16:01,492
Mom will definitely

335
00:16:02,733 --> 00:16:04,252
take you home as soon as possible.

336
00:16:06,093 --> 00:16:06,892
You should

337
00:16:06,893 --> 00:16:07,852
head back now.

338
00:16:08,373 --> 00:16:09,012
Baby.

339
00:16:09,013 --> 00:16:11,452
If they find out, it'll be trouble.

340
00:16:28,253 --> 00:16:29,252
Take good care of him.

341
00:16:30,013 --> 00:16:31,012
Don't worry.

342
00:16:46,733 --> 00:16:47,492
Wait!

343
00:16:52,013 --> 00:16:52,852
Over there.

344
00:17:03,253 --> 00:17:04,052
Get in.

345
00:17:04,053 --> 00:17:04,812
We need to talk.

346
00:17:06,253 --> 00:17:07,812
What do we have to talk about?

347
00:17:10,013 --> 00:17:11,252
Help me get rid of Zhou Quan.

348
00:17:11,253 --> 00:17:13,732
Once the He family takes over the Zhou family business,

349
00:17:14,013 --> 00:17:16,492
I'll ensure your family of four leaves Wu County safely.

350
00:17:16,973 --> 00:17:18,252
You'll never worry about money again.

351
00:17:20,933 --> 00:17:22,012
Why should I trust you?

352
00:17:37,333 --> 00:17:39,092
I'll give you a loaded gun.

353
00:17:39,533 --> 00:17:40,212
Money.

354
00:17:40,693 --> 00:17:41,252
Freedom.

355
00:17:42,053 --> 00:17:43,212
A weapon to protect yourself.

356
00:17:43,693 --> 00:17:45,652
How's that for a win-win situation?
